XTandemSpectrumMatcher
public interface ISpectrumMatcher

org.systemsbiology.xtandem.scoring.ISpectrumMatcher This is a strategy pattern to implement how spectra are traversed looking for matching peaks - because the spectra can be reloaded, the presumption is that any object will be reused and any state will be reset by a new load User: steven Date: 1/19/11
